{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id064307de-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d","identifier":"/us/usc/t19/s4101"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4101"},"text":"§ 4101.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Findings and action on goods of CAFTA–DR countries","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id064307df-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d","identifier":"/us/usc/t19/s4101/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Effect of imports","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If, in any investigation initiated under chapter 1 of title II of the Trade Act of 1974 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2251"},"text":"19 U.S.C. 2251","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], the Commission makes an affirmative determination (or a determination which the President may treat as an affirmative determination under such chapter by reason of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1330/d"},"text":"section 1330(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":"), the Commission shall also find (and report to the President at the time such injury determination is submitted to the President) whether imports of the article of each CAFTA–DR country that qualify as originating goods under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s4033/b"},"text":"section 4033(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":" are a substantial cause of serious injury or threat thereof."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id064307e0-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d","identifier":"/us/usc/t19/s4101/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Presidential determination regarding imports of CAFTA–DR countries","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In determining the nature and extent of action to be taken under chapter 1 of title II of the Trade Act of 1974 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2251"},"text":"19 U.S.C. 2251","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], the President may exclude from the action goods of a CAFTA–DR country with respect to which the Commission has made a negative finding under subsection (a)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id064307e1-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/53/tIII/s331"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–53, title III, § 331","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2005-08-02"},"text":"Aug. 2, 2005","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/119/494"},"text":"119 Stat. 494","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id064307e2-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"prospectiveAmendment","id":"id064307e3-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Termination of Section","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For termination of section by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/53/s107/d"},"text":"section 107(d) of Pub. L. 109–53","children":[],"tail":", see Effective and Termination Dates note below."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id064307e4-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id064307e5-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Trade Act of 1974, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/618"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–618","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-03"},"text":"Jan. 3, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/1978"},"text":"88 Stat. 1978","children":[],"tail":". Chapter 1 of title II of the Act is classified generally to part 1 (§ 2251 et seq.) of subchapter II of chapter 12 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s2101"},"text":"section 2101 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id064307e6-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id064307e7-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective and Termination Dates","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective on the date the Dominican Republic-Central America-United States Free Trade Agreement enters into force (","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-03-01"},"text":"Mar. 1, 2006","children":[],"tail":") and to cease to have effect on the date the Agreement ceases to be in force with respect to the United States, and, during any period in which a country ceases to be a CAFTA–DR country, to cease to have effect with respect to such country, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/53/s107"},"text":"section 107 of Pub. L. 109–53","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s4001"},"text":"section 4001 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
